News,=E2=80=9D International Journal of Social Sciences and Humanity =
Studies 6/1 (2014).</div><div class=3D"">=E2=80=A2 &nbsp;Zeev Volkovich =
&amp; Renata Avros, =E2=80=9CText Classification Using a Novel Times =
